{"tid":2415736,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國學者宋琛留美研究 涉隱瞞共軍背景被控多罪","createTime":"2021-02-20T13:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T13:13:11.000Z","uid":179729,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b6eeacfe56879acd55a65cb7618d7459b0294a","tid":2415736,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/us-fraud-02202021064318.html/@@images/6e37e454-7c3c-492e-b4aa-7afb2b33b50a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fus-fraud-02202021064318.html%2F%40%40images%2F6e37e454-7c3c-492e-b4aa-7afb2b33b50a.jpeg&h=ed0bedc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>FBI調查發現，宋琛主動破壞與解放軍有聯繫的證據。</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前史丹福大學中國訪問學者宋琛（Chen Song），原本被美國控以「簽證欺詐」（visa fraud ) 接受調查。美國聯邦大陪審團當地時間周五（19日），加控宋琛「妨礙司法」、「銷毀文件」和「在美期間隱瞞解放軍的身份並作虛假聲明」等罪，定於4月12日開審。控方指，如果證據確鑿，宋琛入罪，可保護美國大學免受非法外國勢力干擾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5058257660915378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fposts%2F5058257660915378&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=1ba615fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5058257660915378</a>"},{"pid":"603174d326f4fa6aec9e7ade19da0ccb4cf85760","tid":2415736,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"死刑啦屌<br />\n唔係放走佢呀"}]}